1 Open terminal

------------- Install php dependencies -----------

2 Once if necessary Install composer 
php composer-setup.php --install-dir=bin

3 Once Download dependencies
Cd [dossier]/app/
composer install

------------- Install Node js dependencies -----------

3 Once if necessary Install YARN
brew install yarn

----------------------

#Once install des packages:
yarn install

----------------------
When you modify project:

1 cd [ glisser le dossier sources]
2 gulp

# result :
# lunch localhost:3000
# Check your sources assets scss,js and omg and build your product assets
# reload when you modify files and rebuild twig, css or js
# write "gulp deploy" for sync your folder by ftp ( if you have edit a right id and pass on gulpfile.js)
